messages.content:
Invite propagated in a few channels:

Opened a new Discord server, titled "hindu-vidya", to cover mail-streams/ channels I frequently use, including mailstreams such as hindu-vidya, meta-indology, kannada, tamil, shabda-shAstram etc.. You're welcome to join / try it out - https://discord.gg/KGk558erJV . (More context - https://groups.google.com/g/hindu-vidya/c/PKYw3X--7wM)

Nothing special really about this app (Certainly better than whatsapp groups, but that's a very low bar). Just that contributors to https://ambuda.org/ , with whom I communicate frequently, are there - so thought of making wider use of it.

messages.content: नमो नमः। अहं MVR शास्त्री । बङ्गलूरूनगरे वसामि। संस्कृतशिक्षणे, पुरातनग्रन्थानां digitization, अद्वैतवेदान्ते, संस्कृतभाषायाः लौकिकस्वरूपे , संस्कृतक्षेत्रे धनार्जनाय नूतनावसरकल्पने इत्यादिषु विषयेषु मम रूचिः वर्तते।
भो भो सज्जन! मादृशान्य् एव भवतो रुचयः। क्व बॆङ्गळूरुनगरे वासः? अहं सहकारनगरे ऽस्मि। digitization=शब्देन पृष्ठचित्रग्रहणम् अभिप्रेतम्, अथवा +उट्टङ्कनपरिष्कारादिकम्?
